These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
House: gothic-revival, cottage, townhouse, cape-cod
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, pall-mall, swisher, ritmeester
1. the cottage house is somewhere to the right of the gothic-revival house##5
2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker##3
3. the tiparillo-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the left of the ritmeester-smoker##5
5. the tiparillo-smoker is the cottage house##1
6. the townhouse house is the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| House      | cape-cod  | gothic-revival | cottage  | townhouse |
| Cigar   | swisher | ritmeester      | tiparillo | pall-mall |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, prince, aristoff, bongani
House: modern, gothic-revival, palace, colonial
1. the prince-smoker is between the modern house and the colonial house##2
2. the bongani-smoker is somewhere to the left of the colonial house##5
3. the modern house is on the right of the palace house##1
4. the modern house is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
5. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Cigar   | bongani | aristoff | prince   | montecristo |
| House           | palace      | modern    | gothic-revival | colonial      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
House: palace, farmhouse, modern, futuristic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, skiing, snowboarding, biathlon
1. the farmhouse house is the person who's sport is skiing##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the modern house##3
5. the futuristic house is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
6. the farmhouse house is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| House        | farmhouse | palace | modern     | futuristic |
| Sport   | skiing  | biathlon   | snowboarding | badminton    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, metal, rock, trance
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, december, april, november
1. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of metal##1
2. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##5
3. the fan of punk is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who's birthday is in december##2
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
5. the person who's birthday is in november is the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Music-Genre         | rock | punk | metal | trance |
| Birthday   | november   | april     | december    | may       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, guinea-pig, goat, rabbit
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, puzzles, camping, video-games
1. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
3. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Pet          | goat | rabbit   | hedgehog   | guinea-pig    |
| Hobby   | puzzles  | video-games | collecting | camping |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
4 different games are played: go, monopoly, whist, domino
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, aristoff, fonseca, bolivar
1. the person playing domino is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing go is somewhere to the left of the bolivar-smoker##5
3. the bolivar-smoker is between the person playing domino and the fonseca-smoker##2
4. the person playing whist is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Game           | go | monopoly | domino | whist |
| Cigar   | fonseca        | bolivar     | siglo       | aristoff   |

