.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-7::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, weightlifting, cricket, cycling
House: gothic-revival, modern, wooden, colonial
1. the modern house is the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the wooden house##2
3. the gothic-revival house is in an even position##4
4. the colonial house is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##5
5. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the modern house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Sport   | weightlifting | skiing  | cricket  | cycling   |
| House           | colonial  | gothic-revival | wooden | modern |

