.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, photography, video-games, filmmaking
There are 4 different nationalities: american, mexican, indian, brazilian
1. the mexican is on the right of the brazilian##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
5. the indian is somewhere to the left of the american##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Hobby   | photography     | filmmaking | video-games     | cooking   |
| Nationality    | brazilian | mexican  | indian | american |

