.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-9::.
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, mexican, turkish, chinese
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, freelancer, security-guard, social-worker
1. the security-guard is on the right of the argentine##1
2. the turkish is on the left of the chinese##1
3. the argentine is on the left of the turkish##1
4. the mexican is somewhere to the right of the social-worker##5
5. the freelancer is somewhere to the right of the nurse##5
6. the nurse is somewhere to the left of the security-guard##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | argentine | turkish | chinese   | mexican |
| Job       | nurse       | security-guard   | social-worker | freelancer |

