.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, scientist, fisherman, chef
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, cauliflower, mango, plum
1. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the scientist##5
2. the person eating mango is the fisherman##1
3. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the scientist##1
4. the chef is somewhere to the right of the person eating mango##5
5. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the left of the person eating artichoke##5
6. the person eating artichoke is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
7. the fisherman is somewhere to the right of the person eating artichoke##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Job   | mechanic | scientist   | fisherman | chef     |
| Food   | cauliflower     | artichoke | mango  | plum |

