.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-12::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, iris, aconite, azalea
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, board-games, hiking, cooking
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an even position##4
3. the person who growsazalea is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
4. the person who growstulip is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the person who growsazalea is somewhere to the right of the person who growsaconite##5
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Flower   | tulip | aconite        | azalea        | iris |
| Hobby         | hiking  | cooking | photography | board-games |

