4. the person eating eggplant is the owner of the ferret##1
5. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5
6. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person eating watermelon##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
