The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, june, march, november
1. the owner of the hamster is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the fish is on the far left or far right##3
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is in an even position##4
5. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5
6. the owner of the hamster is between the owner of the bird and the person who's birthday is in june##2
7. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Pet      | bird   | hamster  | guinea-pig      | fish       |
| Birthday   | march | november | june | september |

