4 different pets are kept: dog, rabbit, hedgehog, goat
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goat##5
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is the owner of the goat##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Hobby   | board-games     | puzzles | video-games | dancing |
| Pet     | rabbit | dog    | hedgehog    | goat |

