.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-18::.
4 different games are played: bridge, poker, whist, mah-jongg
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, blood-red, mauve, turquise
1. the person who likes mauve is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who likes amber is somewhere to the right of the person who likes turquise##5
3. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the left of the person playing bridge##5
4. the person who likes amber is somewhere to the left of the person playing poker##5
5. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
6. the person playing bridge is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person who likes blood-red##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Game      | whist     | mah-jongg | bridge     | poker |
| Color   | mauve | turquise  | amber | blood-red        |

