.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-19::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, pop, reggae, electronic
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, card-games, woodworking, skydiving
1. the fan of punk is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the fan of pop##2
2. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the fan of electronic##5
3. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
5. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre         | reggae   | electronic   | punk       | pop   |
| Hobby   | woodworking | card-games | chess | skydiving |

