.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, fuchsia, grey, lavender
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, satire, martial-arts, western
1. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere to the left of the person watching satire movies##5
2. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching family movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching satire movies##5
5. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
6. the person who likes chestnut is between the person who likes lavender and the person watching family movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Color        | fuchsia     | lavender | chestnut | grey |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | western | satire      | family        |

 